                  <additions>
                    <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#iv"/> Excerpt from the ordinary of the Mass</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#104r #121v #122r #122v #123r #125v #127r"/> The different prayers of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሠራዊተ፡ መላእልቲሁ፡</foreign> of the different anaphoras</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#123v #124r"/> Suggestion of alternative prayers in the anaphoras</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#126r #126v"/> Imposition of the hand of the Anaphora of the 318 Orthodox Fathers</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#127r"/>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayers, copied for <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢዮብ፡</foreign>, purpose not clear</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#127v #128r #128v"/>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer for help in learning, stained with water,
                          with incipit
                          በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘይበልሕ፡ እምሰይፍ፡ ወእመላጺ፡ ኤልባሕኮን፡ ዘኮነ፡ አኃዜ፡ ኵሉ፡ ወ[.]ተፈታሕ፡ ልበ፡ በኃለ፡ ዝንቱ፡ አስማተከ፡ ዝብርህ፡ ፮አዕይንተ፡ ልብየ፡ ወ፮አዕይንተ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ለአንብቦ፡ ወለተርጕሞ፡ ወለቃለ፡ ድርሰት፡...
                        </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#129r"/> Imposition of the hand of the Anaphora of Our Lord</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a8">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#129v"/> Isolated names</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a9">
                           <desc>Overlooked lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#13r #15v #23r #26r"/>, etc.);
                        and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted
                        (<locus target="#32r #50v #71r #75r #85v #86v #93r #98r #101r"/>), and in another case where the symbol +
                        is used (<locus target="#73r"/>)</desc>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>The codex has been rebound in some disorder; some missing texts have been copied in different hands</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc>
                              <locus target="#ir"/> blank</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>Splice of page: f. 7</desc>
                        </item>
